race.comment: DON'TDOUBTHELADY (1) is a speedy filly who returned from a break with a win over 1300m at this track. Should park just off the speed and is sure to be in the finish. FABULEAN (3) stuck on well last start to finish third over 1200m here after showing good early speed. Ready to go a couple better. HONOURBEFORE GLORY (2) was prominent throughout when winning fresh over 1100m at this circuit. Should be prominent despite the awkward gate and shapes as one of the main contenders. THE KOBAY TRAIN (4) turned in a nice effort to score two runs ago but couldn't follow that up last time out when fifth over 1200m at this course, beaten 5.5 lengths. Best figures measure up so deserves another chance.
